        <summary>Closes this connection gracefully.</summary>
        <remarks>
          <para tool="javadoc-to-mdoc">Closes this connection gracefully.
 This method will attempt to  flush the transmitter's
 internal buffer prior to closing the underlying socket.
 This method MUST NOT be called from a different thread to force 
 shutdown of the connection. Use <c><see cref="M:Org.Apache.Http.IHttpConnection.Shutdown" /></c> instead.
</para>
